   178тЖТ/**
   179тЖТ * POST /integration/webhooks/maximo
   180тЖТ *
   181тЖТ * Receive CM/WO status updates from Maximo.
   182тЖТ *
   183тЖТ * This endpoint is called by Maximo when:
   184тЖТ * - Work order status changes (WAPPR тЖТ APPR тЖТ INPRG тЖТ COMP тЖТ CLOSE)
   185тЖТ * - Work order is cancelled (CAN)
